(101, 2, 'https://d1q70pf5vjeyhc.cloudfront.net/predictions/a6360fb9c1a540f682534017132fe549/1.png', 'The red Ferrari SF90 Stradale transitions from the open highway into a tunnel still slick with rainwater, its headlights piercing the dim environment with intense white beams. Reflections of tunnel lights ripple across the wet car surface and the soaked road beneath. The tunnel walls gleam with moisture, and mist swirls at tire-level as the car speeds through, leaving trails of vaporized rain in its wake.\nEvery droplet clinging to the vehicle is illuminated in detail, while the roar of the engine vibrates through the confined space, visually represented by subtle atmospheric distortion. The Ferrari‚Äôs sleek aerodynamic lines cut through the tunnel like a bullet, emphasizing speed and elegance.\nCamera follows in dynamic motion tracking, showing side, rear, and low-angle shots that highlight the splash physics under artificial lighting. Water droplets scatter and catch the light, forming bokeh effects in the background.\n\nStyle: cinematic tunnel sequence, wet reflections, volumetric lighting, speed blur, atmospheric haze, ultra-detailed water behavior, dynamic angles, immersive realism, 4K ultra clarity.', '2025-07-19 20:05:59'),
(102, 2, 'https://d1q70pf5vjeyhc.cloudfront.net/predictions/12da525b18dc44e88f3b91650c5635f6/1.png', 'As the Ferrari SF90 Stradale exits the tunnel at high speed, it bursts into an open mountain road surrounded by misty pine forests. Rain intensifies, cascading down the windshield in fast-moving streams. Thunder rumbles in the distance as flashes of lightning briefly illuminate the landscape, casting dramatic shadows across the road and car surface.\nThe vehicle‚Äôs red paint glistens with a mirror-like finish, now coated with droplets and streaks. Puddles on the winding road splash high into the air with every turn, captured in slow motion. Trees blur in the background due to motion, while the foreground remains razor-sharp, enhancing the speed sensation.\nCinematic drone angles follow the car from above and behind, showing the winding road ahead, glowing brake lights reflecting off the wet terrain, and atmospheric fog rolling across the scene. The entire moment feels like a climactic chase scene in a high-budget film.\n\nStyle: cinematic action realism, nature-rain fusion, thunderstorm lighting, ultra-slow-motion splash physics, dramatic contrast, aerial tracking shots, 4K HDR film look.', '2025-07-19 20:09:17'),
(103, 2, 'https://d1q70pf5vjeyhc.cloudfront.net/predictions/2dc85cab712543fcbd9e48b30a01acf2/1.png', 'Berikut adalah beberapa opsi prompt yang bisa Anda gunakan, disesuaikan dengan gaya dan detail yang Anda inginkan:\n\nOpsi 1: Realistis & Hangat\n\n\"Photorealistic close-up of a child\'s hands holding an Indofood sausage, natural daylight, shallow depth of field, warm color palette, focus on the sausage and child\'s hands, soft background of a kitchen counter, high quality, detailed, 4k\"\n\n*   Fokus: Realisme, kehangatan, detail pada produk dan tangan anak.\n*   Cocok untuk: Menekankan kualitas produk dan momen keseharian yang akrab.\n\nOpsi 2: Ceria & Bermain\n\n\"Digital art illustration of a smiling child holding up an Indofood sausage, bright and cheerful lighting, vibrant color palette, playful composition, simple background with cartoon elements, focus on the child\'s expression and the sausage, high quality, detailed, 4k\"\n\n*   Fokus: Keceriaan, ilustrasi digital yang menarik, komposisi yang menyenangkan.\n*   Cocok untuk: Menarik perhatian anak-anak, kesan produk yang menyenangkan.\n\nOpsi 3: Klasik & Dramatis\n\n\"Oil painting of a child holding an Indofood sausage, dramatic lighting, rich and deep color palette, Rembrandt-style portrait, dark and moody background, focus on the child\'s face and the sausage, high quality, detailed, 4k\"\n\n*   Fokus: Gaya lukisan klasik, pencahayaan dramatis, kesan mendalam.\n*   Cocok untuk: Tampilan artistik yang unik, kesan produk yang berkelas.\n\nOpsi 4: Minimalis & Modern\n\n\"Photorealistic product shot of an Indofood sausage being held by a child\'s hand, clean and minimalist composition, soft and diffused lighting, neutral color palette, blurred background, focus on the sausage and the hand, high quality, detailed, 4k\"\n\n*   Fokus: Kesederhanaan, modernitas, detail produk yang menonjol.\n*   Cocok untuk: Menekankan kualitas produk dengan tampilan yang bersih dan profesional.\n\nTips Tambahan:\n\n*   Anda bis