(30, 2, 'https://d1q70pf5vjeyhc.cloudfront.net/predictions/48c9ec98a77447e4ac178159309004d1/1.mp4', 'As the Ferrari SF90 Stradale exits the tunnel at high speed, it bursts into an open mountain road surrounded by misty pine forests. Rain intensifies, cascading down the windshield in fast-moving streams. Thunder rumbles in the distance as flashes of lightning briefly illuminate the landscape, casting dramatic shadows across the road and car surface.\nThe vehicle‚Äôs red paint glistens with a mirror-like finish, now coated with droplets and streaks. Puddles on the winding road splash high into the air with every turn, captured in slow motion. Trees blur in the background due to motion, while the foreground remains razor-sharp, enhancing the speed sensation.\nCinematic drone angles follow the car from above and behind, showing the winding road ahead, glowing brake lights reflecting off the wet terrain, and atmospheric fog rolling across the scene. The entire moment feels like a climactic chase scene in a high-budget film.\n\nStyle: cinematic action realism, nature-rain fusion, thunderstorm lighting, ultra-slow-motion splash physics, dramatic contrast, aerial tracking shots, 4K HDR film look.', '2025-07-19 20:10:43'),
